  NOTE --> CONTROL
  NOTE --> INGRESS
  NOTE --> RTDL
  NOTE --> CASELABEL
  NOTE --> LEARNING
  NOTE --> OPSGOV
  NOTE --> TRANSPORT

  GHA -->|authenticates through| OIDC
  GHA -->|dispatches| SFN
  SFN -->|assigns and persists| RUNID
  SFN -->|writes control receipts to| RUNCTL
  SFN -->|publishes orchestration signals to| CTRLBUS
  CTRLBUS -->|transported by| MSK
  SFN -->|starts bounded replay| WSP

  OBJ -->|provides replay basis to| WSP
  RUNID -->|pins active run scope for| WSP
  RUNID -->|pins active run scope for| IGLAMBDA
  RUNID -->|pins active run scope for| RTDL
  RUNID -->|pins active run scope for| CASELABEL
  RUNID -->|pins active run scope for| LEARNING
  RUNID -->|pins active run scope for| RUNCTL

  WSP -->|pushes ingress load to| HTTPAPI
  HTTPAPI -->|invokes| IGLAMBDA
  IGLAMBDA -->|deduplicates in| IGDDB
  IGLAMBDA -->|writes failure disposition to| IGDLQ
  IGLAMBDA -->|publishes admitted traffic to| TTRAFFIC
  TTRAFFIC -->|transported by| MSK
  GLUEREG -. enforces schema compatibility for .-> TTRAFFIC

  TTRAFFIC -->|feeds promoted RTDL intake boundary| RINTAKE
  RINTAKE --> TCTXA
  RINTAKE --> TCTXE
  RINTAKE --> TFLOW
  TCTXA -->|consumed by| CSFB
  TCTXE -->|consumed by| CSFB
  TFLOW -->|consumed by| CSFB
  CSFB -->|binds context for| IEG
  IEG -->|supplies graph truth to| OFP
  OFP -->|supplies features to| DF
  DF -->|emits decisions to| DL
  DL -->|appends decision truth to| DLA
  DL -->|feeds archival evidence to| ARCH
  DL --> TDEC
  DL -->|emits case-worthy decision truth to| CTRIG
  CTRIG -->|opens or reuses cases in| CM
  CM -->|commits authoritative labels to| LS

  DLA -->|provides runtime decision evidence to| OFS
  CM -->|provides case-linked truth to| OFS
  LS -->|provides authoritative supervision to| OFS
  OFS -->|builds bounded learning basis for| MF
  MF -->|commits train/eval evidence to| MPR
  MPR -->|publishes governed active bundle truth as| ACTIVEBUNDLE
  ACTIVEBUNDLE -->|resolved by live runtime for| DF

  ACTIVEBUNDLE -->|challenged by operator drift checks in| DRIFTCHK
  RUNCTL -->|reconstructed through| DRIFTCHK
  EVID -->|read back by| DRIFTCHK
  CW -->|feeds live operator view in| OPSDASH
  OPSDASH -->|links operator action chain to| RUNBOOK
  RUNBOOK -->|authorizes bounded standby / restore through| IDLECTRL
  IDLECTRL -->|returns active runtime to governed truth for| DF
  IDLECTRL -->|returns case/label path to governed truth for| CM

  ARCH -->|stores evidence in| EVID
  DLA -->|stores proof continuity in| EVID
  CM -->|stores case evidence in| EVID
  LS -->|stores label evidence in| EVID
  OFS -->|stores dataset-basis evidence in| EVID
  MF -->|stores train/eval evidence in| EVID
  MPR -->|stores promotion / rollback evidence in| EVID
  RUNCTL -->|stores proof receipts in| EVID

  IGLAMBDA -->|reads active handles from| SSM
  WSP -->|reads active handles from| SSM
  RTDL -->|reads active handles from| SSM
  CASELABEL -->|reads active handles from| SSM
  LEARNING -->|reads active handles from| SSM
  IGLAMBDA -->|emits logs and metrics to| CW
  WSP -->|emits logs to| CW
  RTDL -->|emits logs and metrics to| CW
  CASELABEL -->|emits logs and metrics to| CW
  LEARNING -->|emits managed telemetry to| CW
  SFN -->|emits logs and metrics to| CW
  CW -. exposes operator visibility for .-> RUNCTL

